  "translations": {
    "en": "As for the companion's right, accompany him with bounty and fairness. Honour him as he honours you. Do not let him outdo you in generosity. Wish for him as he wishes for you, restrain him from sin. Be mercy, not punishment. There is no strength save in Allah. As for the partner's right, if absent look after his affairs, if present show regard. Make no decision without him, do nothing without consulting. Guard his property, betray him not. Allah's hand is over two partners who do not betray each other. There is no strength save in Allah.",
